On Sunday, June 5th, Dr. Truax brought to a close the year's work with a student class which has been engaged since last September in studying the Bible as literature. The text book used was one of the series of\ The Modern Reader's Bible\ edited by Prof. Moulton of the Uni-versity of Chicago.
